<i>I can't go out alone</i>

26:00.440 --> 26:02.320
<i>I go over it a thousand times</i>

26:02.400 --> 26:08.240
<i>I look for potions</i>
<i>But I don't find solutions</i>

26:08.840 --> 26:10.640
<i>Trapped</i>

26:10.720 --> 26:12.960
<i>I see it clearly</i>

26:13.040 --> 26:16.640
<i>It's all in my head</i>

26:22.720 --> 26:24.560
Charly, that rap was awesome.

26:24.640 --> 26:26.800
-That was great.
-Thanks, guys.

26:28.560 --> 26:30.480
So this is where you hide out.

26:31.320 --> 26:33.240
This storeroom has history.

26:33.320 --> 26:35.800
Come. I'll show you
what Sky Vibes will be like.

26:36.320 --> 26:38.240
A stage will be here.

26:39.000 --> 26:40.440
The bar will be over there.

26:40.520 --> 26:43.360
And in this area
will be tables for the audience.

26:43.880 --> 26:46.040
Look. This was Sky Vibes.

26:48.160 --> 26:49.480
This was Sky Vibes?

26:54.360 --> 26:55.200
Luz.

26:56.200 --> 26:58.960
-We should go. Shall we?
-Yeah.

26:59.040 --> 27:00.800
-What can I help you with?
-The box.

27:00.880 --> 27:03.080
One for Nati and one for you.

27:12.520 --> 27:13.520
Let's go, Tony.

27:14.520 --> 27:15.560
Yeah, let's go.

27:22.320 --> 27:25.400
Can you tell me what you're doing here
on my vacation, Dad?

27:25.480 --> 27:27.800
-I can't believe it.
-I told you, Steffi.

27:27.880 --> 27:31.120
Ian insisted. We wanted to see
you compete, and you never let us.

27:31.200 --> 27:34.400
-Don't involve Ian in this.
-Dad misses you when you're gone.

27:35.880 --> 27:38.440
We wanted to surprise you.
You know I never do this.

27:38.520 --> 27:41.480
This is the first time.
Plus, I thought it would be fun.

27:41.560 --> 27:44.320
We used your grandma's last name
so you wouldn't know.

27:44.400 --> 27:47.040
And it didn't occur to you
to ask me what I wanted?

27:47.120 --> 27:50.440
Or warn me at least?
I don't get what you're trying to do.

27:50.520 --> 27:51.640
Definitely not this.

27:52.160 --> 27:53.800
And you're lying too.

27:53.880 --> 27:56.800
This is my trip, Dad,
not a family vacation.

27:56.880 --> 27:59.720
And you know that.
I can't believe you're doing this.

28:01.200 --> 28:03.200
Sorry. I'm really sorry.

28:03.280 --> 28:05.960
I thought you'd like us here
supporting you.

28:06.040 --> 28:08.240
Leave tomorrow or I will.

28:09.880 --> 28:11.320
But I'm staying.

28:16.760 --> 28:18.840
This is for table three. All right.

28:24.360 --> 28:25.400
Luz.

28:28.680 --> 28:29.520
You're the same.

28:30.520 --> 28:31.360
You too.

28:33.040 --> 28:35.200
Antonio, how was the first day?

28:36.240 --> 28:37.680
Better than I expected.

28:39.120 --> 28:43.040
I was thinking
maybe Luz could be our guide.

28:44.560 --> 28:45.400
My classes.

28:45.480 --> 28:47.400
Charly and Julián can cover for you.

28:48.920 --> 28:50.560
I really appreciate it.

28:51.480 --> 28:52.320
Thanks, Luz.

28:56.200 --> 28:57.480
Luz.

28:59.080 --> 29:00.960
Give it your all for Steffi.

29:01.040 --> 29:04.520
She's our only hope
and our most important competitor.

29:04.600 --> 29:06.120
You can count on it, Augusto.

29:06.200 --> 29:07.400
You're amazing.

29:30.920 --> 29:33.400
Hello, everyone.

29:34.280 --> 29:36.280
Hi. How are you all?

29:36.360 --> 29:38.280
Welcome.

29:38.880 --> 29:43.360
Today is the beginning
of a new season at Cielo Grande.

29:46.480 --> 29:48.080
This year's very special for us

29:48.160 --> 29:51.440
because, as you know,
with a lot of effort and happiness,

29:51.520 --> 29:54.200
we're bringing back Summer Crush.

29:56.680 --> 29:57.520
Yes.

29:58.480 --> 30:02.560
Summer Crush!

30:02.640 --> 30:06.000
Yes, after 12 years,
the competition is back at Cielo Grande.

30:06.080 --> 30:09.360
I'd like to give special thanks
to our wonderful team.

30:10.120 --> 30:11.240
Charly…

30:14.760 --> 30:16.080
who brings happiness.

30:16.160 --> 30:18.320
Luz, you're the soul…

30:19.800 --> 30:21.280
The soul of Cielo Grande.

30:22.840 --> 30:26.000
Julián, you're like a son to me.

30:29.800 --> 30:35.360
I'm excited and happy.
I wish us an unforgettable season.

30:40.920 --> 30:42.920
-Let's go, Augusto.
-No!

31:11.120 --> 31:13.280
PASSWORD
